      *
     CSR         ESB200    ENDSR
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      *                                                    *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     CSR         #SB210    BEGSR
      *
     C           *IN03     DOUEQ*ON
      *
     C                     EXFMTDSP01
     C                     SETOF                     3199
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   MSG
      *
     C           *IN03     IFEQ *ON
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           D1WKCD    IFEQ *ZERO
